   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "9c1f5a1b-500b-460f-93c6-4d430290f56d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Hyperparameter-Tuning (z. B. mit GridSearchCV)"
   ]
  },
